    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it is a total stunner! This car is in truly incredible shape; it\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
